Open with: "Dwelling Fire is for rental or non-owner-occupied properties. Let me get the property details."
 
# QUESTIONS — ask in order, one per turn
 
Q1: "What's the address of the rental property?" → {DF_PropertyAddress}
Q2: "What's the property's approximate replacement cost?" → {DF_DwellingValue}
Q3: "Is the property currently rented, vacant, or seasonal?" → {DF_OccupancyStatus}
Q4: "How long has it been a rental property?" → {DF_YearsAsRental}
Q5: "Year built and construction type?" → {DF_YearBuilt}, {DF_ConstructionType}
Q6: "Do you screen tenants and require renters' insurance?" → {DF_TenantPolicies}
Q7: "Any prior claims at this property?" → {DF_ClaimHistory}
Q8: "Is the property in your name personally or in an LLC?" → {DF_OwnershipStructure}
 
# RISK FACTORS TO CAPTURE
- Vacant > 30 days → underwriter review.
- No tenant screening → MEDIUM minimum.
- LLC ownership → may require Commercial Property quote instead.
 
