Q6: "What's the value of livestock, if any?" → {FO_LivestockValue}
Q7: "Do you have any farm employees or seasonal workers?" → {FO_FarmEmployees}
Q8: "Have you had any farm-related losses in the last 5 years?" → {FO_LossHistory}
